{"tid":133393,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【金正男未死？】死者肚腩冇紋身 日媒：可能係替身","createTime":"2017-02-24T14:35:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-24T15:45:51.000Z","uid":7824,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c1ee63943dd4e00e92b50c4d301a5d22eac0f94e","tid":133393,"uid":7824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T14:35:11.000Z","msg":"北韓領導人金正恩哥哥金正男上周一在馬來西亞被殺，驗屍初步結果顯示，在金正男臉上和眼上驗出VX神經毒劑。但有日本傳媒報道，由於死者身上沒有紋身，懷疑他並非金正男。<br />\n<br />\n日本富士電視台公開一張金正男於2013年拍攝的照片，他在照片中赤裸上身，樣貌與日前曝光的死者照片相似，只是多了鬍子，但富士電視台發放的照片中，男子的手臂和腹部都有紋身，和死者不同。報道事件的富士電視台女記者藤田水美表示，她和金正男曾見面、採訪和吃飯，次數不下30次，而紋身照片正正是金正男傳給她。<br />\n<br />\n而日本新聞網站「brandnew-s」的報道指，對金正男遭暗殺後的照片表示懷疑，認為死者可能根本不是金正男。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170224/56349072\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170224%2F56349072&d=6pEOCw3Iqoz%2FZ73NBW83J2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=83e75f26\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170224%2F56349072&h=9e664b70\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170224/56349072</a><br />\n愈黎愈複雜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fd7b20b9bc30e666d7027ef0e038eeff9c84f3b","tid":133393,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T15:41:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i405.photobucket.com/albums/pp135/gintamahost/131e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi405.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fpp135%2Fgintamahost%2F131e.jpg&h=18b7bd6e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ed963d2acf8a40395682330a27f84b0805562881","tid":133393,"uid":52743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T15:45:51.000Z","msg":"豬一樣既隊友"}]}